// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3871 — Mass File Rename (incransom)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 16535143-bc99-5957-a700-8b21d802ce9f

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
